title: Whataburger Oh Whata Night
text:
5:00 p.m. Wednesday, Oct. 28, 2015 Categories 
Events, Fundraisers, Kids | Family On Wednesday, Oct. 28, Whataburger customers can show their support for the Americas High School swim team by enjoying their favorite menu items, and 20 percent of Whataburger’s sales from 5 to 8 p.m. will be donated to the team. Whataburger’s “Oh Whata Night” will also include its popular “Whataburger for a Year” drawing, where one customer’s name will be drawn to win the prize – a free Whataburger each week for an entire year. To add to the fun, there will also be a photo booth at the event. Related
